title: Q: The Winged Serpent (1982 Fantasy) David Carradine, Richard Roundtree

sources.title: Q: The Winged Serpent (1982 Fantasy) David Carradine, Richard Roundtree
sources.description:
NYPD detectives Shepard and Powell are working on a bizarre case of a ritualistic Aztec murder. Meanwhile, something big is attacking people of New York and only greedy small time crook Jimmy Quinn knows where its lair is.

Director & Writer: Larry Cohen

Main cast:
Michael Moriarty - Jimmy Quinn
David Carradine - Detective Shepard
Richard Roundtree - Detective Powell
Candy Clark - Joan
Malachy McCourt - Commissioner

Genres: Horror, Crime, Fantasy, Thriller
Release date: October 29, 1982 
Filming location: New York City, USA
